    "body": "Ok, so I did a lot of testing and there is some conflict with `babel-register`. It is somehow causing `require('path/to/cached/compiler')` to hang in the loading strategy [here](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/blob/develop/packages/truffle-compile/compilerSupplier/loadingStrategies/VersionRange.js#L37) and blow the heap. When I comment out `require('babel-register')` in the Truffle config, it is able to successfully compile. I'm not sure what we're going to do about this but we'll try and see what we can do for these to peacefully coexist :)",
